            Candidates 
        



 






              Careers
              





 















Why should YOU join Constellium? 


 Every day, our near 11,000 employees fuse their diverse talents, experiences and ideas to develop and produce the world-leading aluminium products and solutions for which Constellium is renowned.As a newly independent company with a new direction and vision in place our company today offers you an unrivalled opportunity to help us shape and define our future form, position and course.From production engineers to support functions, we are seeking talented, passionate and committed individuals who are as excited about the possibilities of aluminium as we are.In this section, you can find detailed overviews of our jobs, browse our vacancies and apply, as well as meet our human resources managers and read employee testimonials.



























