 |  
                                            				    Work with us 
				                                            


 






              Work with us
              



Each day our approximately 11,000 employees are inspired to shape and be part of Constellium’s future. By working with Constellium, you too can draw inspiration from our unique vision, values, attributes and commitments that set us apart from the competition.Our vision and valuesAs a team and with the support of all our stakeholders, we want Constellium to become the most profitable company in our industry. To achieve this goal, we will rely on:

 team work and mutual trust;
 entrepreneurship and decisiveness;
 sense of urgency and decentralized decision making;
 responsibility and accountability;
 rigor and discipline;
 transparency and highest standards of ethics.


  We will strive relentlessly for value creation through growth, operational improvement and innovation in all aspects of our business.We will respect, develop and protect our people, serve our customers, and write our future together.Our attributes

 Technical challenges: innovate and create solutions that meet the rigorous specifications of our clients working at the forefront of major industries including aerospace, automotive and packaging.
 Innovative materials: push the boundaries and capabilities of aluminium, a 100%-recyclable material with almost endless applications.

  

 Safe operating environment: gain reassurance working with a company where safety is anchored in our culture and always at the forefront of our thinking.
 History and culture: be motivated as part of a new company that traces its history to the beginning of aluminium production, and which has built on a Lean culture of safety, best-in-class customer portfolio, commercial and operational excellence, innovation and talent.
 Human values: join a global team where employees are visible, talent is nurtured and respect is universal.
 Career opportunities: develop your career with mobility opportunities that range from product and process development, to R&D, EHS, Lean transformation, sales, etc.

Our commitments

 Delivering excellence: Constellium’s workforce shares the common ambition to deliver value and efficiency in all its activities. This is one of the reasons that we count among our customers some of the world’s largest and most respected companies.
 Creative collaboration: Constellium works with customers to forge strong, integrated partnerships and transform creative concepts into high-quality, actionable solutions.
 Advancing innovation: Constellium sets the industry standard, generating value by virtue of our expertise and innovation.
 Excellence in EHS: Constellium’s respect for people and the environment in which we live governs our priorities and drives our reputation as a company.

 























